Want to learn more about Wolf game? Here are some resources.

Alpha game whitepaper: https://t.co/5YvxjmqZTo
Community guide (created by @TerminatusX): https://t.co/4VKBSxCUOl

Once you have your $WOOL follow these steps to play:
1 - Go to https://t.co/kZl0jtMn12
2 - Connect your wallet
3 - Click the pack you want to join
4 - Scroll down and there will be a button to stake your $WOOL (beware you will have to pay gas again)
5 - Done, you're in!

$WOOL is the currency of the game and you can buy and play with any amount. You can buy $WOOL by going to the link below and swapping $ETH for it. Beware that you will have to pay gas to swap.

https://t.co/UL43gnsH5B

You can join a pack with a wolf, sheep, or $WOOL. Every place even the last place has a prize allocated to it. The prize gets spread among the pack depending on how much they have contributed. So lower-ranked packs will win less but will also have to share less.
